buttonctrl v0.0.4

* Change the way `INPUT` vs `INPUT_PULLUP` is configured.

buttonctrl v0.0.3

* Pass some input parameters as template arguments as to simplify the default
  case during initialisation

buttonctrl v0.0.2

* Allow customisation of pressed state (HIGH vs LOW)
* Allow to configure input pin as pullup

buttonctrl v0.0.1

* Initial release
